E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Of course you did. How is the old girl? Still the same spark?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~意料之中啊。老情人怎么样？还有爱的火花吗？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I seen him, yeah. Not much though.
~z~Ah, Johnny boy, how's it going out there?
~z~Yo, Johnny. How it going? Lost MC still giving it to 'em?
~z~Yes they have and they might be about to get a whole lot shitter.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~确实如此，而且情况还可能变得更糟。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~That the same Ash you ain't seeing no more? The Ashley Butler who's too tweaked to know what's good for her?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~又是那个再也不见的Ash？犯毒瘾犯到失去判断力的Ashley Butler？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Just when you thought shit couldn't get worse...
~z~That's why I didn't become a politician. So long, sport.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~所以我才没有成为政客。再见了，哥们。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I wish it didn't have to be this way, but we don't got much choice.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我不希望变成这样，但我们也没得选。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Those that're worth having behind you, at least.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~至少那些值得信赖的弟兄会支持你。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Well things should be better for a whole heap of people.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~很多人的人生都不该如此的。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Hey, Angus. You seen much of Billy yet?
~z~we'll give it a go. Good luck, sport.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我会试试看的。祝你好运，哥们。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Fuck, I seen what it does to some of the brothers, man.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~操，我知道几个吸冰毒的兄弟的下场，老兄。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~More shit storm than steam room, Congressman. We weren't all born into money.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~烂得没空去蒸汽浴室，议员。不是所有人都生来富贵的。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Jonathan. That export guy we got, he don't have no more bike orders at the moment.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~Jonathan。问我们收车的人，他暂时不需要摩托了。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Johnny? What's this I hear about you getting caught up with the mafia?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~Johnny？我怎么听说你和黑手党走一块儿去了？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~That Ashley, sure. I just want her to be okay so I ain't leaving her to die, you know.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~是那个Ashley，没错。我只是不想见死不救，让她能保住小命而已。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Beyond that, I'll probably try to cut my ties.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~除此以外，可能还会断掉一些人际关系。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Yeah, well, I'd prefer to stand up for something then to chop and change and stab a friend in the back to get ahead.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~是吗，比起出尔反尔过河拆桥，我倒宁可坚守自己的信念。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Yeah, I know it, but you know me, always had a soft spot for someone in trouble.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~是啊，我也知道。你了解我的，见不得别人陷入窘境。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Listen, Stubbs, things have turned to shit.
~z~Hey, Brian fucking started it. No, wait, fucking Billy started it.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~喂，Brian才是导火索。不对，Billy才他妈是。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Such a shame your values are more suited to medieval times.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~可惜你那套三观更适合中世纪。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Yeah, I don't know what the committee would think of your body art, personal hygiene or "fuck you" attitude, but,
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~好啊，不知道委员会对你的身体艺术、个人卫生和「操你妈」的态度有什么看法，但是，

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Don't want some fed with a stick up his ass connecting the dots, you know?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我不想让哪个麻烦的探员发现我俩的关系，懂吧？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~No, some of us married into it. Ha ha ha.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~确实，有些人是嫁入豪门。哈哈哈。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~The only spark left is in her meth pipe. That shit's killing her.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~她只剩下冰毒吸管里的火花了。冰毒害了她。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~so I'm gonna sound how I like, that being my fucking presidential right.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~所以我就要说这种话，这是会长的权利。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~If money, drugs and assholes are fun for you, then maybe. I just like old fashioned robbing.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~如果你喜欢钞票、毒品和混蛋，那确实。但我喜欢老派的抢劫。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Sure does, Johnny. Well, why don't you have yourself some fun, hmm? Liberty City's a good place for that.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~当然了，Johnny。要么你自己去找点乐子？自由城可是个好地方。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~That's because you're way down in your chair, Angus, and it's hard to see ya.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~谁让你现在坐轮椅呢，Angus，不低头都看不见。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~But you're still helping her out of fixes? If it's over you got to end it completely.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~那你还在劝她戒毒？真分了就利落点。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I dunno, man. We'll see. Catch you round, huh?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~不知道，兄弟。慢慢来吧。回头见吧。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I just hope you weren't getting massaged.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~别是做按摩的时候想找我吧。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I mean he'd hardly make eye contact since I got hurt.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~出车祸后他都没看过我几眼。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~And some people killed for it. You got any work for me, man?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~还有人因钱而死。你这儿有活吗，伙计？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Alright, man. I'm just saying, do what's best for the brothers. Not what's best for your pride.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~好吧，兄弟。我只想说，多为弟兄们考虑，别光顾着自己的面子。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~My, my, A man of principle. Impressive, Klebitz. You must find Liberty City an awful place to live!
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~天哪，有原则的人。厉害啊，Klebitz。你一定和自由城的生活格格不入吧！

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Think it's probably best for both of us to keep some distance now.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我们两个现在最好保持一些距离。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~If you love her enough, you can help her.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~要是爱得够深，你还可以去帮她。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Klebitz, listen, briefly wanted to touch base and thank you for your recent assistance.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~Klebitz，听着，有事跟你说一声，顺便感谢下你先前的协助。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Ashley? The ice got her good - I finally cut her loose in my head, man.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~Ashley？她毒瘾太重了，我终于能放下她了，伙计。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~turn on brothers and your world turns to shit.
~z~I'm president of a burnt out house and some broken ass brothers. It's dead, man. It's over.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我这会长据点被烧、兄弟尽失。已经完了，伙计。都结束了。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~You're a good man, Johnny. Things should have worked out better for ya.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~你是个好人，Johnny。你的人生不该是现在这样的。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I see your problems have been resolved. Is it back to normal at The Lost Motorcycle Club?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~你的问题好像都解决了吧，失落机车俱乐部现在回到正轨了吗？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Johnny, I was just thinking about you.
~z~Nah, brother. Shit got fucked. Too much craziness, we couldn't hold it together.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~不，兄弟。都他妈完了。过于疯狂了，我们撑不住了。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Well, now that you mention it, there might be a few things that need to be handled discreetly.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~被你这么一说，好像是有些需要悄悄解决的活。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Man, oh, man. What women can do to us. Don't get in over your head, Johnny.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我的天哪。女人的魔力啊。可别被冲昏头脑，Johnny。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~That crown feeling heavy, is it? For what it's worth, I'd follow you, man. I'm sure the other brothers will too.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~皇冠果然很重吧？无论如何，我支持你，兄弟。相信弟兄们都是如此。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I don't know what's left for her other than that need to fuck up everything around her.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~都不知道她脑子里还剩什么，只会把一切搞得一团糟。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~... you go and start a civil war.
~z~Damn that's a real fucking shame, man. And too fucking bad. So what you doin' with yourself?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~妈的，真他妈可惜啊，兄弟。太他妈糟了。现在一个人干啥呢？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Jonathan. What's happening in the world of the walking?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~Jonathan，你这走地人有什么新故事吗？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Well, I'm president of a bunch of Alderney piss lickers, not the whole nation,
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我不过是一群Alderney马屁精的头头，不是美国总统。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Those that ain't gonna stab me in the back. You gonna go see Billy? I don't think I can after what he said.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~也是那些不会背刺我的弟兄。你去探望Billy吗？他说了那种话，我可能去不了了。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Call me if you feel up to it, sport. Bye now.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~有兴趣就联系我吧，哥们。拜啦。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Please call back. We thank you for your business.

E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我会的。你也保重，兄弟。多保重。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Yeah, well, Ash... she introduced me to this guy.
~z~It's past that, dude. We're over. Long gone.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~早就没感情了，兄弟。已经分了。早分了。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I dunno. I'll probably keep sending money to Jim's old lady and her kid, I owe him that.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~不知道。可能会每月给Jim的老婆孩子生活费吧，我欠他的。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Well, dude, what do you think? Is he on top of his shit or is he gonna run this club into a hole?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~那老兄，我问问你，你觉得他会振兴帮派还是带来麻烦？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~You see, we got a set of codes that mean you can't keep on like nothing's happened after brothers
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~你看，我们帮会有一套规矩，一旦兄弟反目秩序崩塌，

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Billy doesn't see anything that he don't wanna.
~z~He'll see anything within smoking, fucking and drinking proximity, but he won't see the two ton truck bearing down on him.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~他的眼里只有吸毒、日逼还有喝酒，根本看不见朝他开过来的大卡车。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Due to minor technical difficulties, Bellic Enterprises cannot accomodate you with a vehicle.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~由于某些技术故障，Bellic集团无法为您安排车辆。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~He wouldn't want me there either. Adios, John boy. Chapter president.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~他也不会希望我去的。再见了，阿强。分会会长。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~That mobster is cold as all hell. Look after yourself, man.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~那个黑手党可是冷酷无情的。自己保重，兄弟。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~He's gonna run himself into some hole, I know that. Shit, Billy doesn't really talk to me.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~反正他肯定会自讨苦吃。妈的，Billy真没怎么跟我聊过。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Alright, man. I'll see you there. But don't expect no rubdowns.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~好的，伙计。会所见。恕不提供按摩啊。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~We need to talk. how about I come to you clubhouse?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~我们该谈谈了。要么我来你们会所一趟？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~I heard. How you feel about the chapter presidency?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~听说了。分会会长的体验如何？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Sure, sure, so are you gonna put me up for membership of your little sauna club, now that I've helped you out?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~当然，当然。既然我帮了你那么多，你那桑拿俱乐部是不是该给我登记个会员了？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Oh. Does that mean I'm gonna have to find something else to pursue in my free time?
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~噢。那我是不是只能找点别的事打发时间了？

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~Ha ha ha. That'd be a damn sight funnier if I didn't think it was true, John.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~哈哈哈哈。可惜这就是现实，我笑不出来。

E1MF2AU.original: ~z~It don't work out that way, do it? Adios, amigo.
E1MF2AU.translated: ~z~可惜天不如人意啊，不是吗？再见了，兄弟。
